cal CRM-system, which implements a number of functions that take into account the needs of large business companies: tools for managing projects and processes taking place in the company; integration with corporate systems; work from one','<p>analytical CRM-system, which implements a number of functions that take into account the needs of large business companies: tools for managing projects and processes taking place in the company; integration with corporate systems; work from a single interface and other functionality.</p><p>Software class: Organizational process management systems, Information systems for solving specific industry tasks</p><p>Added to the Unified Register of Russian Programs on September 6, 2016</p><p>The owner is a Russian commercial organization LIMITED LIABILITY COMPANY \"1C\", The rights were transferred from CJSC \"1C\" to LLC \"1C\" as an additional contribution to the authorized capital of LLC \"1C\" under the Agreement on the alienation of the exclusive right to computer programs dated December 09 2010.</p>',3,'en'),(466,'Prime Source','We are implementing an automated business process management system based on IBM BPM and FICO BPM so that banks and financial organizations manage and improve processes more efficiently, achieve strategic goals through modeling, execution and control.','<p>It is a single end-to-end business process management platform with an efficient set of tools for building, testing and deploying business processes.</p><p>Prime Source is the only Kazakh company with the status of an IBM Platinum Partner. This allows us to provide the best prices on the market and provide customers with quality services and competencies.</p><p>Thanks to the formed team of the best specialists, we have achieved the minimum implementation time and the maximum speed of time-to-market changes.</p>',64,'en'),(467,'MindSales CRM','CRM offers a complete solution, so there is no need to purchase modules from different vendors','<p>MindSales CR