ing programs for veterinarians, clinics, offices and pharmacies, more than 1000 veterinary clinics from small offices to chains. With the mobile application of the veterinary program VetManager the doctor always has all the information he needs to work: scheduled appointments, patients\' medical records, invoices. This greatly saves the doctor\'s time at the reception, which will allow him to pay attention to more patients. It has a user-friendly interface and efficient management on your phone. It is also an indispensable thing on call!</p>',362,'en'),(581,'ВЕТСОФТ-ВЕТЕРИНАР','The company \"VETSOFT\" is engaged in business automation in the areas of humanitarian and veterinary medicine.','<p>Very often when managing a veterinary clinic, you want to see visual information on changes in the average check, revenue, etc. We have provided such a possibility in the Statistics module. This module contains visual charts and reports which are required for efficient management. Added additional functionality in the creation of the doctor\'s work schedule. Modification of the pricing of clinics with the possibility of accounting for third-party services. Print price lists from the Registry module. Functionality that automates the activities of laboratories has been implemented.</p>',363,'en'),(582,'Ansoft','The company focuses on the following priority areas: software development for the automation of business tasks (AVARDA brand); developments for integrated automation in the field of commerce','<p>Ansoft is a Russian developer and supplier of information systems for business automation. The company was founded in 1992 and owns the AVARDA brand. Its main specialization is the complex automation of wholesale and retail trade. Ansoft has a regional representative office in Nizhny Novgorod and a software development center in Volgograd. Among Ansoft\'s clients are SIA International, Rusbiznesavto, Ecco, Finn Flare, BauCenter, E-House and other leading companies.</p>',354,'en'),