ogram.</p>',366,'en'),(586,'WMS Logictics Vision Suite','LOGISTICS VISION SUITE - RECOGNIZED IN THE GARTNER MAGIC SQUARE 2021 FOR WMS. More than 20 years on the market of WMS solutions. Leading position in EMEA (Central and Eastern Europe, Russia, Turkey, Israel and Middle East)','<p>Logistics Vision Suite (LVS / LVision) is a high-performance, flexible, adaptive WMS system with advanced functionality and powerful configuration and adaptation tools, designed to manage warehouse operations with a variety of business processes, handling and storage methods. The system is designed to manage warehouses that require the ability to rationally and automatically manage warehouse operations with an emphasis on improving the processes of physical warehouse operations.</p>',378,'en'),(587,' 	1С:Фитнес клуб','The 1C:Fitness Club CRM system is used by every third fitness club and sports studio in Russia. Suitable for fitness clubs, stretching and Pilates studios, dance and martial arts schools, crossfit studios and swimming pools. 2,000+ Clients have already ch','<p>The program has two basic reports: a sales plan for the month for each employee and the percentage of its fulfillment, as well as a plan of calls - how many are scheduled, how many are executed.</p><p>The sales manager will be able to create a plan for each employee to interact with customers, to analyze the effectiveness of sales of members by managers.</p><p>Report on the leads in the context of the results of tasks and stages of sale allows you to expand and customize the sales funnel CRM-system for in-depth analysis of the effectiveness of managers.</p><p>In system it is possible to create the reports which allow to estimate, what actions of managers and in what volume transit to the certain result, and to make the decision on improvement of certain types of interactions with the client.</p><p>Creation of managers\' ratings on conversions and types of interactions: meeting, guest visit, incoming and outgoing call. Analysis by data from the CRM system of employees on the conversion of leads into sales allows to study and transfer their experience to colleagues.</p><p>For the fitness club marketer, a report in the CRM system on the primary customer contact to the end result (win/loss) will be useful. Identification of actions that lead to a transaction or rejection, which allows you to prepare recommendations for the sales department.</p><p>The instructor sees data on visitors to his training sessions. Suggest the most appropriate training program based on the data contained in the client card in the CRM.</p><p>The implementation of mobile applications in the club\'s business processes not only simplifies the work of the staff, but also increases the loyalty of customers who choose the convenience of signing up for classes via phone.</p><p>The CRM system makes it easy to set up a membership term trigger and send a personalized offer without losing a customer.</p><p>Access to sections of the system can be flexibly set up with rights for each employee and keep records of all changes. This will help eliminate retroactive changes.</p>',367,'en'),(588,'FitBase','A cloud-based service for automating a fitness club or studio. CRM with built-in funnels and autotasks, accounting system, online appointment widget and mobile application for clients.','<p>The ideal service for fitness clubs, sports sections and gyms. FitBase works from your computer and phone, integrates with cash register equipment and ACS.</p>',368,'en'),(589,' 	Mobifitness','Management system for fitness club, sports studio, dance or yoga school: 4 necessary functions in one system - accounting, mobile application, online recording for the website and social networks.','<p>Mobifitness is the technological leader in solutions for fitness clubs and sports studios.</p><p>With Mobifitness, every fitness club, sports studio, dance or yoga school can afford its own accounting system, mobile app, quality class schedule and other products that optimize employee workflow and increase customer loyalty and sales.</p>',369,'en'),(590,'UNIVERSE-Фитнес','Multifunctional CRM system, solves a number of problems in a fitness club: the organization of sales, customer membership, staff payroll, stock and financial accounting. ','<p>is a new cloud-based service. UNIVERSE-Beauty, UNIVERSE-Medicine, UNIVERSE-Denta, UNIVERSE-Fitness are local programs that are installed on your computer. Both options have their pros and cons. Local products have more than 15 years on the IT market, they have pretty extensive functionality, deep and sophisticated analytics (over 100 reporting forms), all data are stored on your computer, no permanent access to the Internet, one-time payment for the license. Cloud crm-system UNIVERSE-CRM - has a unique modern design, a necessary set of basic functions and reports, access is possible from various devices from anywhere in the world, the minimum subscription fees, free trial version.</p>',370,'en'),(591,'Pocket Sport','CRM-system for working with clients, booking classes, waiting list, record of sales of goods, services, subscriptions and gift certificates ','<p>Using CRM system and site from Pocket Sport allows to increase conversion rate. It is much more convenient to organize work with users and supervise activity of administrators now. Clients can quickly find all the necessary information and sign up for training, but it is always possible to adjust the system to any of their wishes. Cloud-based system to automate the management of sports studios: online and offline workouts; customer records and waiting lists; notifications and mailings; advanced marketing tools; e-subscriptions; online recording; mobile applications.</p>',371,'en'),(592,'AppEvent',' A cloud-based solution for event accounting and collaboration between attendees. Unites all event participants in one place.','<p>The AppEvent booking widget allows customers and partners to book you without calling ahea