eveloping our training programs rather than manually counting payroll.</p>',377,'en'),(599,'Buhta: WMS','The \"Buhta VMS\" warehouse management system allows: Optimize warehouse processes; Manage the warehouse in real time; Obtain information about the state of the warehouse and the workload of human resources promptly;','<p>Key features of the WMS system:</p><p>Together with the WMS warehouse management software you get a solution that can be refined as the business grows and needs. This can be done by your specialists or by asking for help from us.</p><p>The warehouse management system is customized to your unique and specific tasks.</p><p>Short deployment times</p><p>Short terms of implementation</p><p>Account of contracts of responsible storage</p><p>Calculating storage fees (billing)</p><p>Tracking performance rates</p><p>Barcoding</p>',381,'en'),(600,'BEAUTY PRO','Beauty Pro beauty salon software solves all current problems and improves management efficiency.','<p>CRM for Beauty Pro salon - information about clients and their visits is always at your fingertips. Never before has there been such order in documentation, from visitor records to reporting. Keep statistics, make the right managerial decisions, and run your business quickly and efficiently!</p>',380,'en'),(601,'FloraPoint','CRM system for the flower business, which contains a warehouse and accounting','<p>FloraPoint helps you actively attract and retain customers with advanced loyalty systems. Take advantage of all available tools or integrate your own. Florapoint system provides full-fledged work with pre-orders of your customers with reminders in the calendar. Don\'t lose control of order fulfillment and delivery, especially during the holidays! Take into account every petal and assemble your bouquet in 15 seconds. History of changes in arrangements. Set a free price for a bouquet. Additional mark-ups for florists\' services. Reassembly and disassembly of bouquets. Keep sales records for absolutely all goods (cuttings, gifts and related products, bouquets, complete sets and services). The real picture of sales is always at your fingertips anywhere in the world.</p>',385,'en'),(602,'Roboseller','Automate the processes of sports schools and training centers, increase sales using Roboseller tools','<p>CRM-system for sports schools and training centers. Keeps records of clients and season tickets, controls staff work, attendance, payments, generates schedules, reports, SMS- and WhatsApp-mailings. Management and sales in one CRM.</p>',387,'en'),(603,'NanoGym','Full automation of the manager, sales department, administrators and trainers, payroll, more than 20 reports for the owners. CRM for fitness club!','<p>Online workouts can be added to your fitness schedule at NanoGym. You can hold both personal and group classes. The accounting of visits to online training sessions and deduction of payment from the client\'s subscription is carried out automatically. In the client\'s personal account there is an online schedule, his online visits are displayed, there is an opportunity to pay.</p>',388,'en'),(604,'ФОЛИО WMS','FOLIO WMS allows you to automate the processes of reception, placement, storage, processing and shipment of goods in warehouses, warehouse terminals, industrial and commercial warehouses.','<p>The warehouse automation system helps to optimize the placement of goods for storage so that warehouse space and employees are used most efficiently. The system can manage the work of warehouse equipment and personnel, control the movement of cargo and loading equipment around the warehouse area, and promptly schedule tasks for personnel based on the current situation.</p><p>It is integrated with a number of popular warehouse accounting programs, including 1C:. There is extensive experience of integration with other - non-standard customer accounting systems.</p>',382,'en'),(605,'Gym One','A simple and effective way to manage a sports center','<p>Gym One - a comprehensive automation of all aspects of the fitness center: customer records, season tickets management, personnel management, training records, retail and warehouse, monitoring key performance indicators of the fitness center and much more.</p>',389,'en'),(606,'HelloClient','The program for those who provide services. Work with clients and orders in one place.','<p>Assign employees responsible for the order. Set statuses, add jobs and goods to the order, and accept payment. Print the receipts. Control all cash transactions. Know how much money is in your cash register. Manage your merchandise. Keep up-to-date with balances and items requiring purchases. Data on all activities by orders, employees, customers, sales and warehouse.</p>',390,'en'),(607,'POSIFLORA','Suitable for everyone: small flower studios, large online stores and networks. ','<p>Increase sales of your store, control all important store indicators, manage your customer base and loyalty program. Automatic integration with Internet-shop and social networks. Warehouse control and reduction of write-offs: you know exactly which flowers sell better, and you don\'t buy unnecessary things.</p>',391,'en'),(608,'Проксима Склад WSM','“Проксима-Склад WMS” is a modular system that pays for itself very quickly. It allows you to manage the warehouse. The system is adapted to the needs of the business. It has a full set of functions that help to optimize management.','<p>This WMS allows you to manage your warehouse online. Particularly good results are shown in warehouses with a large number of terminals for data processing and with a significant flow of goods.</p><p>Interfacing with corporate information systems is not too difficult. \"Proxima-Storage\" can be modified to meet the needs of the customer. This became real due to the open software code. The logic of business processes is clearly traceable.</p><p>The interface is made intuitive. Thanks to this the staff quickly adapts to the use of new technologies. Inventory is possible without affecting other processes.</p>',383,'en'),(609,'INSPIRO','The INSPIRO system has been managing large businesses and trading systems across the country for 20 years.','<p>One system for everything - orders, customers, CRM, warehouse, logistics, storefront, online store, finance. All data on your sales, merchandise, warehouse is stored in your personal database. Complete and accurate report on write-offs from the warehouse. Maintenance of networks is not a problem, INSPIRO automatically collects data and will help you control florists, watch sales for each salon, track deliveries and remains.</p>',392,'en'),(610,'Торговля цветами','The program \"Trade in Flowers\" was developed on the platform 1C:Enterprise and is designed to automate the business of trade in flowers and floristic services. The program is designed to keep records in the enterprise with all the necessary set of reports','<p>The program \"Trade in Flowers\" is developed on the platform 1C:Enterprise and is designed to automate the business of trade in flowers and floristic services. The program is designed to keep records in the enterprise with all the necessary set of reports and tools for productive work, to obtain operational information and help in decision-making.</p>',393,'en'),(611,'AVARDA.WSM','AVARDA.WMS is a software product designed to manage any type of modern warehouse.  AVARDA.WMS is based on the powerful automation system AVARDA','<p>When developing AVARDA.WMS, all the advantages of the basic system were retained.</p><p>AVARDA.WMS optimizes all main warehouse processes, allows to achieve maximum efficiency of warehouse space utilization, ensures highly productive, accurate and well-coordinated warehouse operation. The system efficiently manages all technological operations in the warehouse in real time: it independently organizes the work of warehouse equipment and personnel, controls the movement of cargo and loading equipment within the warehouse area, and promptly plans tasks taking into account the current situation.</p>',384,'en'),(612,'FloraPOS','Thanks to invaluable experience and ideas of our partners FloraPOS has no competitors in the market of floristry automation and constantly expands its functionality for maximum convenience','<p>FloraPOS is perfect for automation of both a small florist salon and a large retail chain of salons (including those with salons in different cities)</p><p>The main advantage of FloraPOS is its full adaptation to the everyday processes of florist business i.e:</p><p>Sale and return of goods</p><p>Making bouquets</p><p>Product markdown (including multiple markdowns)</p><p>Write-off of goods and partial writing-off of bouquets</p><p>Inventory (full and partial)</p><p>Preliminary order and client base management</p><p>Flexible loyalty system</p><p>Integration with online stores and CRM</p><p style=\"margin-left: 20px;\">Integration with courier and logistics service</p>',394,'en'),(613,'Бизнес.Ру','One cloud-based program that covers 95% of all modern business needs','<p>Ready-to-use solutions for all popular retail and service businesses. Automate the work of your store at all stages of its activities, from convenient work with suppliers and automation of the purchasing process of goods, to building a system of loyalty and control over the work of salesmen in online mode. Organization of the sales department, both in the area of wholesale supplies, as well as in the area of services. CRM system with integrated telephony and request collection from the site with direct access to stock levels. Ready templates of KP, Contracts and letters to customers, with integrated mailing system and the possibility of end-to-end sales analytics by channel.</p>',395,'en'),(614,'Tillypad','Business owners do not need to be present in the office or request reports from employees - Tillypad will send reports to the mail with the results of the restaurant.','<p>Tillypad is an automation system for restaurant, cafe, bar or chain of catering and entertainment facilities. Tillypad automation solves a range of problems associated with the administration and optimization of business processes, production, personnel and management accounting, reducing costs and increasing the profitability of the restaurant business of any type and scale. With Tillypad you can improve the efficiency of your establishment and increase its profits.</p>',396,'en'),(615,'CWSM-3000','CWMS-3000® is a system for automation and management of warehouse operations, allowing real-time control of all technological operations at the warehouse, as well as billing (calculation) of warehouse services and other services.','<p>The system manages the work of warehouse personnel, controls the movement of goods, and promptly plans tasks for personnel taking into account the current situation.</p><p>The CWMS-3000® is an expert system capable of independently making recommendations for optimizing all warehouse technological processes and coordinating the work of personnel and material handling equipment in order to achieve maximum efficiency in the use of warehouse space and to increase the productivity of work in the warehouse.</p>',386,'en'),(616,'NOMIA POS','A new automation system for restaurants, cafes and bars, which will take your establishment to a higher level.','<p>Nomia POS is a new restaurant automation system. Nomia has been developed for 3 years by a team with great experience in retail and restaurant market. Advanced technologies from the sphere of foodtech and b2c sales are used in its development and implementation. Unlike conventional automation systems, Nomia offers optimization at the level of all processes in your restaurant, cafe or bar!</p><p>Service features:</p><p>- Customized analytics allows you to build the best strategy for restaurant development and growth of your income.</p><p>- Clever one2go interface motivates waiters to sell the most profitable dishes and allows you to quickly create an order in 3 clicks.</p><p>- Integrate Pos into your mobile app - you can access the system from any device.</p><p>- Adding new modules in one click.</p><p>- No more searching for suppliers in person - you have access to a constantly growing base of trusted Nomia partners.</p><p>- Free connectivity and maintenance.</p><p>- Reasonable cost, no need to buy a license.</p>',399,'en'),(617,'Quick Resto','Unified system for guest service, in the hall, by pre-order or with delivery of meals','<p>Discounts, promotions, specials, combos, subscriptions - these and other loyalty programs in CRM will help to increase the average check and attendance at the time you need. Café and restaurant management and accounting software allows you to set up your desktop so that you can quickly find out your priority business metrics: top 5 dishes, revenue by employee, average check or others. Control the business and plan revenue with a clear comparison of indicators with previous periods - day, week, month, year.</p>',400,'en'),(618,'LeClick','CRM system for restaurants is a personal office, where you can see and process new reservations online,','<p>The CRM system for restaurants is a personal office in which you can see and process new reservations received by the restaurant online using reservation forms posted on the leclick.ru website, the restaurant\'s website and/or Facebook, and partner sites. Reservations received by phone are entered by the hostess into the system, the electronic equivalent of a book of reservations. All information about guests (name, phone number, e-mail), the number and status of reservations, and the status of the guest is stored in a personal cabinet. The system functionality allows you to generate reports on the occupancy of the establishment, the effectiveness of services, with which a particular restaurant cooperates, to do targeted SMS and E-mail mailings.</p>',401,'en'),(619,'СКИФ','Представляем Вам облачную систему СКИФ - комплексное решение для