f the attached file, as well as by various search criteria.</p>',177,'en'),(726,'Microsoft Sharepoint','Smart mobile intranet Manage and share content, data and apps. Give employees in your organization the ability to easily interact with each other and quickly find the information they need.','<p>Collaborate easily and work together seamlessly. With SharePoint, a project team, department or division can create and customize its own site for efficient and dynamic collaboration. Share files, data, news and resources. Set up your site and make team work easier. Use Windows PCs, Macs and mobile devices to collaborate freely with colleagues and employees from other organizations in a protected environment. Use the intranet to bring your team together and set up a corporate messaging system. Improve efficiency by giving employees access to resources and applications through homepages and portals.</p>',127,'en'),(727,'Naudoc','easy to implement and use electronic document management system for medium-sized businesses and public authorities. NauDoc is designed to automate the sending and receiving of correspondence, internal documents ','<p>The system is supplied with open source code. All components of the system are included in the delivery and do not require purchase of additional licenses (such as DBMS, operating system and other software products of third-party developers). NauDoc is a cross-platform system, which allows using both UNIX and Windows infrastructure for work. NauDoc interface is based on web technologies and does not require installation of software on workstations, works on tablets, has a mobile application for smartphones.</p>',128,'en'),(728,'LanDocs','Russian platform for enterprise content management, for 20 years LanDocs platform provides effective management of electronic documents in the largest organizations in Russia and CIS countries.','<p>LanDocs electronic document management system</p><p>Development of LANIT, a software platform for buildin