fectiveness from the first month of use.','<p>The \"Shop-Success\" production management system is guaranteed to increase efficiency in the following business processes:</p><p>Production. The use of a QR-coded sticker on products with complete information on all stages of processing, including information on personnel, makes the production process transparent, rhythmic and easy to control. Responsibility and motivation of the personnel increases manifold, and analysis of causes of defects becomes open, fast and shared by all members of the team.</p><p>Use of equipment. Automation of production control makes it possible to use the full potential of the equipment, successfully maneuvering its load, minimizing downtime and timely carrying out maintenance, which will prolong its service life.</p><p>Standardization of key procedures and operations. ERP will bring order into the technological part of production, providing information for the development and improvement of technological charts. Standardization of processes due to ERP system allows to raise product quality to a new level.</p><p>Remuneration system, personnel motivation and production discipline. With ERP all production processes become transparent, the head of the system will be able to adjust the wage system, managing the bonus part. For the workers, the payment system becomes clear, and the use of piecework motivation schemes increases the dedication of personnel. For the foreman it is an opportunity to shift attention from control procedures to improvement of production, to manage key processes more effectively.</p><p>Salary calculation. Automated ERP-accounting opens the possibility to calculate the salary within a minute. Bonuses and fines system allows to increase the efficiency of each employee.</p><p>Warehouse management. Owing to ERP-system supplying of the company can be brought to automatism for the majority of positions - \"Workshop-Success\" will control material consumption and make an order of the necessary amount according to production plans.</p><p>Dealer network. Partners and dealers connected to ERP will always be aware of the volume of finished and manufactured goods, can send orders from customers in a couple of clicks and accelerate the work of the sales system as a whole.</p>',118,'en'),(740,'WS. ERP','The main advantage obtained from the program - this is a complete automation of accounting and avoidance of manual calculations. ','<p>Implementation of the program allows you to control the document flow to the maximum extent possible and exclude loss of documents. A separate tool for controlling production and orders will reduce costs as much as possible. The ability to create production stages for the company significantly reduces the time of work with counterparties and the warehouse.</p>',119,'en'),(741,'SAP ERP','Intelligent ERP solutions from SAP are the digital core that allows companies to integrate the next generation of complex cross-functional business processes to turn the company into a smart enterprise.','<p>Our cloud-based and on-premises ERP solutions help manage all aspects of operations, from accounting and CRM to supply chain management and procurement.</p>',120,'en'),(742,'Arta Synergy','The efficiency of our solutions is tested daily by more than 150 corporate clients all over the world Ensure a high level of executive discipline Accelerate document flow threefold and reduce office expenses by going paperless.','<ul><li>Function description</li><li>Control of orders</li><li>Administrative workflow</li><li>Personnel records and paperwork</li><li>Report on executive discipline</li></ul><p>What do you need to get started?</p><ul><li>Determine a list of logs and nomenclature of cases</li><li>List of types of documents and their flow routes (journals, files)</li><li>Determine electronic and printed forms of documents</li><li>Define forms for executive discipline reporting</li></ul><p>Synergy Customers is the timely execution of the company\'s sales plan through a set of tools to control it</p><p>Increase sales volume by monitoring the sales team\'s execution of each stage of the transaction. Identify problem areas in sales by analyzing failures at various stages.</p>',140,'en'),(743,'ПАРУС','Solutions that can automate any processes in the field of financial and economic activity, R&D and production management.','<p>Improving the efficiency of contract management under the State Defense Order by automating contract execution control, contract supply management of materials and CRP, control of compliance of actual and planned costs of contracts under the State Defense Order.</p>',122,'en'),(744,'Галактика','is a flexible and modern tool for solving current and strategic management tasks of a modern enterprise in the digital economy.','<p>The system has a high productivity, wide functionality, excellent integration properties and provides employees with reliable information for effective decision-making.</p>',126,'en'),(745,'Word','A word processor designed to create, view, edit, and format texts of articles, business papers, and other documents, with local application of the simplest table forms','<p>a text editor with an original graphical interface, developed at the Xerox PARC research center. Charles Simonyi, the creator of Bravo, left PARC in 1981. That same summer, Simonyi poached Brody, with whom he had worked on Bravo.</p><p>The first release of Word for MS-DOS was in late 1983. It was poorly received by the market; sales were reduced by the presence of a competing product, WordPerfect. The first version was written by Richard Brodie for IBM PCs using DOS in 1983. Later versions were released for the Apple Macintosh (1984), SCO UNIX, and Microsoft Windows (1989).</p>',234,'en'),(746,'Excel','Early on, Excel became the cause of a trademark lawsuit from another company that was already selling a suite of programs under the name \"Excel.\" As a result of the dispute, Microsoft was obliged to use the name \"Microsoft Excel\" in all of its official pr','<p>Microsoft Excel (also sometimes called Microsoft Office Excel[5]) is a spreadsheet program created by Microsoft Corporation for Microsoft Windows, Windows NT and Mac OS as well as Android, iOS and Windows Phone. It provides economic and statistical calculations, graphics tools, and, with the exception of Excel 2008 for Mac OS X, the VBA (Visual Basic for Application) macro-programming language. Microsoft Excel is part of Microsoft Office.</p>',235,'en'),(747,'PowerPoint','Easily and efficiently design slides Create well-designed, effective slides with the PowerPoint Builder and Ideas.  3D technology: from movies to presentations Now you can easily insert 3D objects and embedded animations from your','<p>Microsoft Office PowerPoint (power point) is a presentation preparation and viewing program that is part of Microsoft Office and is available in editions for Microsoft Windows and macOS operating systems, as well as for the Android and iOS mobile platforms. Materials prepared with PowerPoint are designed to be displayed on a large screen - through a projector, or on a large-sized television screen.</p>',236,'en'),(748,'Publisher','Название программы происходит от слова «publisher», то есть программа, рассчитанная на выпуск разнообразных публикаций.Office Publisher содержит новые и усовершенствованные средства, помогающие эффективно создавать, настраивать и многократно использовать ','<p>is a desktop publishing system developed by Microsoft Corporation. It is an entry-level application that differs from Microsoft Office Word in that its emphasis is on designing page layout rather than on layout and text checking. Microsoft Publisher is the software that is part of the Microsoft Office suite.</p><p>The first version of the package was developed in 1991</p><p>By simply browsing through the elements of branding-color, font, emblem, and business information-and applying them to all the contents of Office Publisher 2007, you can get started faster.</p>',237,'en'),(749,'OneNote','(formerly Microsoft Office OneNote) is a program for creating quick notes and organizing personal information, a notebook with a hierarchical organization of entries, can serve as an analogue of the usual notepad. ','<p>The OneNote workspace is a blank sheet of paper where you can take text and handwritten notes, make drawings, and record voice comments. You can also drag and drop information into OneNote from the browser window. There is no \"Save\" icon in this program because the data you enter is saved automatically. Sheets are combined into sections, and sections are combined into notebooks. The list of sheets in a section is on the right side of the current sheet, the list of sections is at the top, and the list of open notebooks is on the left side.</p>',238,'en'),(750,'Outlook','is a personal information manager with e-mail client and Groupware features from Microsoft.  In addition to its email client features, Microsoft Outlook is a full-featured organizer that provides ','<p>Outlook should not be confused with the Outlook Express product. Outlook Express is a free e-mail client built into most versions of Windows released between 1998 and 2003. In Windows Vista, Outlook Express is replaced by Windows Mail; in Windows 7, there is no Windows Mail and instead you can install Windows Essentials, a component of which is Windows Mail Live. Starting with Windows 8 and above, Windows Mail has returned but as a Metro/UWP application.</p><p>There is also Outlook.com webmail, which allows you to view and send mail without having to install Outlook.</p>',239,'en'),(751,'Acsess',' is a relational database management system (DBMS)[2] from Microsoft. It is part of the Microsoft Office suite. It has a wide range of functions, including linked queries, communication with external tables','<p>The main components of MS Access:</p><p>table builder;</p><p>Builder of screen forms;</p><p>Builder of SQL-queries (the SQL language in MS Access does not correspond to the ANSI standard);</p><p>Builder of printable reports;</p><p>database builder/maintenance</p><p>They can call scripts in VBA language, so MS Access allows you to develop applications and databases almost \"from scratch\" or write a shell for an external database, allows you to build key links between queries of tables.</p><p>Microsoft Jet Database Engine, which is used as MS Access database engine, is a file-server DBMS and therefore is applicable only to applications working with small amounts of data and with a small number of users working with this data simultaneously.</p>',240,'en'),(752,' IntoPath','application used to develop XML-based data entry forms. This application first appeared as part of Microsoft Office 2003 in late 2003, and has since been released as part of ','<p>During development, the application was originally codenamed \"NetDocs\", then \"XDocs\". The current version is Microsoft InfoPath 2013.</p><p>The main feature of InfoPath is the ability to create, view and edit documents that support some user-defined XML schema. Connection to external systems - Access databases, MS SQL, web services - can be used to obtain and change data. In addition, because the data is in XML form, documents can be processed by third-party XML processors. Using Microsoft Office Forms Server or Microsoft Office SharePoint Server allows you to work with XML forms through a browser, without installing the InfoPath application on the client.</p>',241,'en'),(753,'Docsvision','Electronic archive of documents of the organization on the platform Docsvision Storage of electronic documents and any content of the company in one system. Fast acquisition of the archive, convenient search, download and upload of files.','<p>Stores primary documents and other financial documents created in the enterprise accounting system or received from counterparties in electronic/paper form. Quickly searches for and downloads documents in response to FTS requests. Reduces the risk of \"advance\" payment of VAT. Reduces document storage costs. Keeps all personnel and personnel reserve documents in a secure database. Automates personnel processes (recruiting, hiring, firing) and consolidates information about employees in personnel files. Accounting and storage of socially important documents in a secure system protected in accordance with the requirements of Federal Law 152.</p>',141,'en'),(754,'Thunberbird','is a free e-mail program that\'s easy to install and configure - and has lots of great features! Thunderbird improves your email experience by combining speed, privacy and the latest technology. Focus ','<p>A host of features, such as \"Tracking Waiver\" and remote content blocking, work together to ensure your security and privacy, so you have peace of mind. With add-ons (extensions and themes) and a host of other features, you can change the view and feel of Thunderbird in an instant. Thunderbird is free and respects freedom, and is fully funded by donations! Help us continue to improve by supporting the project.Stay tuned for the latest news, new features and events, and to learn about upcoming releases.</p>',242,'en'),(755,'win-rar.','The ability to compress files is very important to the digital workspace. We can send more data at higher speeds than ever before, which is why zip files are such a popular business tool around the world. ','<p>Zip is a widely used file-archiving format that is used to compress one or more files in one place, thereby reducing their overall size and simplifying data transfer. Zip files basically work the same way as a standard folder on your computer. However, when you use zipped files, the contents of the folder are compressed, which reduces the amount of data your computer uses. Zip files encode information into fewer bits, thereby reducing the size of the file or files by removing excess data. This is called \"lossless data compression,\" which ensures that all original data is preserved.</p>',243,'en'),(756,' 	Voxlink','Over 800 stations and not a single successful hacking attempt. Millions of calls processed, and thousands of days of uninterrupted server operation','<p>Expensive communication tariffs</p><p>Reduce your expenses on communication by 60% or more: Cost of calls for you will become on mobile throughout Kazakhstan - from 7 tenge, Intercity - from 15 tenge</p><p>Single-channel connection.</p><p>We will help you to transfer your current number to SIP or provide you with a multichannel number with any area code.</p><p>Calls are lost.</p><p>We can set up competent routing of calls according to work scheme of your company. As well as forwarding to a cell phone, notification of missed calls by email and sms.</p><p>No call statistics</p><p>We will set an optimal system of statistics to calculate the quality of your managers\' work</p><p>No record of calls</p><p>Organize record keeping and storage of all phone calls.</p><p>Low level of service</p><p>Your customer base will grow by improving the quality of communication and service.</p><p>No return on advertising</p><p>With installation of statistics and CRM system you will know what advertising really brings profit and customers</p><p>No modern telephony features</p><p>Facilitate and simplify the work of your employees with features such as: call transfer/interception and call hold, real-time listening to calls, prompting, etc.</p>',65,'en'),(757,'ПЛЮСОФОН','The \"Plusophone\" project has been providing IP-telephony services for businesses and individuals since 2012.','<p>We serve 80,000 active numbers and process 90 million minutes of voice traffic per month. Our own communication hubs in 55 major Russian cities enable us to provide our customers with reliable long-distance and international communications. We have 500,000 available numbers. All numbers are available for online connection.</p><p>Realizing that reliable and cost-effective telephony is vital for