ed time interval, the calibration is automatically reactivated. The program uses the geographical position and time of day to match the daily cycle, but both can be set manually.</p>',253,'en'),(817,'Alfresco','Content chaos occurs when documents are stored in multiple places - on paper, on laptops and USB drives, in email and on network drives, and in various repositories and file sharing sites.','<p>Alfresco offers innovative content management solutions that connect, manage, and protect your enterprise\'s most important information wherever it resides.</p><p>With Alfresco\'s open cloud ECM you can manage content from any location, deliver information to users from any location, and deliver applications to any device. Alfresco enables businesses to increase employee productivity, provide valuable information, and deliver exceptional customer experiences.</p>',149,'en'),(818,'Mailbird','is not just an email client. In addition to several unique features that you will never find with competitors, Mailbird is a true \"control center\" for your business.','<p>Mailbird is a desktop email client for Windows 8 and 10 , based on Sparrow Mail Client for OS X .</p><p>It was awarded \"Best Email Software for Windows\" in 2015 and in 2014 and in 2013 by PC World magazine</p><p>The company is headquartered in Livit. Technology startup ecosystem in Bali, Indonesia . In March 2015, Mailbird released version 2.0 with new features such as delayed emails, video meetings and Speed Reader, and added integrations for Facebook , WhatsApp , Veeting Rooms and others.</p>',255,'en'),(819,'WSS Docs','The platform was developed on the basis of Microsoft SharePoint, taking into account the Russian specifics of document flow and is included in the register of domestic software. The system has several editions and a large catalog of additional modules, wh','<p>WSS Docs ECM platform is designed to automate the workflow of documents in different areas: personnel records, paperwork, accounting an