ng to the GTD concept, the main function of the program is to record all desired goals, cases and tasks, and then sort them into different folders. The application window contains a sidebar where folders are located:</p><p>\"Collect\".</p><p>Inbox - this folder is designed to store tasks that have not yet been sorted.</p><p>\"Focus.\"</p><p>Today - this folder contains the most important things to do before the end of the day.</p><p>Next - this folder contains various tasks and projects to be done in the near future.</p><p>Scheduled - this folder contains things to be done when they are due.</p><p>Someday - this folder contains tasks that are worth doing, but do not need to be done right away.</p>',263,'en'),(830,'Cold Turkey Blocker','is a productivity program that you can use to temporarily block yourself from popular social networking sites, addictive websites and games so you can get your work done!','<p>Square sites (whole site or explicit page)</p><p>Square apps</p><p>Squares calendar (make a weekly schedule)</p><p>Set blocking time</p><p>Set secret phrase</p><p>Completely block clients from using PCs</p><p>In any case, if you need to use all these points, you have to pay for its pro-forma Cold Turkey.</p><p>Favorable circumstances:</p><p>Easy to use.</p><p>Free</p><p>Square site with a square description, clock and schedule</p><p>Offer measurements to track online exercises</p>',264,'en'),(831,'MindNode','conventionally speaking, is an electronic board for creating branch diagrams. The design, at first glance, is primitive - at startup there will be literally nothing but a central point. When hovering over it, small pluses are displayed','<p>The width of the block is also configurable. That\'s all the basic functionality. You can add other types of branches - but it\'s better to learn the necessary shortcuts right away, which will allow you to work with a complex document without taking your fingers off the keyboard. Pay attention to the Styles panel, too - you can change the design and set themes there. They are few, but they help diversify the graphics. In addition, you can customize the blocks and tie lines. Particular attention - tab Documents, where they put the settings for displaying text and attachments.</p>',265,'en'),(832,'Intalev','A guarantee of long-lasting partnerships with your clients. INTALEV: Corporate Management is a new ERP-class system designed for efficient document management. ','<p>Management receives an effective tool for controlling the activities of subordinates with the ability to make important management decisions in a timely manner</p><p>The company receives a complete electronic archive of all documents. The process of approving, reviewing, and approving is considerably accelerated.</p><p>Automation of electronic document management based on INTALEV: Corporate Management combines document management, business process management and financial management in a single system.</p><p>Increased executive discipline, processes become transparent to staff and management.</p>',154,'en'),(833,'Pushbullet','a convenient way to send links, text, files on Android. PushBullet is an easy way to quickly transfer files, links, notes, addresses, task lists from your browser to your Android mobile device and back.','<p>PushBullet is an easy way to quickly transfer files, links, notes, addresses, and task lists to your Android mobile device. To start using the service, you need to go to the home page, register with your Google account and install the extension for your browser. After that, you need to install the appropriate app on your mobile device. Your mobile device appears in the list of connected devices on the service page, and you can now send information from your browser to Android and back. For this purpose it is most convenient to use the installed browser extension.</p>',266,'en'),(834,'Bear','is a beautiful and flexible app for taking notes and prose on the go for both iOS devices and Mac OS desktops. KEY FEATURE - Stay organized by linking notes together. - Use hashtags to organize ','<p>ADDITIONAL FEATURES</p><p>- Rich preview during recording, so you see the prose, not the code</p><p>- Advanced markup editor that supports and highlights over 20 programming languages</p><p>- Use cross-references to create the main body of work, a quick link to other notes, etc. Д.</p><p>- Quickly add tasks to individual notes to keep yourself on task</p><p>- Multiple export options including HTML, PDF, DOCX, MD, JPG and more</p><p>- Smart recognition of data items such as links, emails, addresses, colors, and more</p>',267,'en'),(835,'СБИС','Electronic signature and document exchange between companies, within a company and with ordinary people. In СБИС, sign the entire package of closing documents in one click. ','<p>Create bills of lading, invoices as usual or directly in СБИС. One click, and the client has them. He signs them with his electronic signature and sends them to you. In the end, you and the client get a full set of legally signed documents. In the same way, you can send documents not only to companies but also to employees and even ordinary people, regardless of whether they are registered in SBIS or not. The tools built into СБИС allow you to create and edit office (Word, Excel) files and accounting documents (invoices, invoices, advance reports) on any device: phone, tablet or computer. With СБИС you can view and sign them even without an Internet connection.</p>',155,'en'),(836,'FocusList','FocusList is available for both Mac and iPhone, and the basic idea is very simple. Start your day by listing what you need to do during the day, and choose an interval of time that you would like to devote to that task. ','<p>FocusList allows you to do more in-depth work. FocusList is your one stop app for planning your day and increasing your productivity with 25-minute intervals, time schedules and memories.</p><p>Features:</p><p>Plan: Start your day by planning your activities throughout the day. Give each task a grade. Plan throughout the day and make sure everything on your list gets done.</p><p>Focus: Do tasks in 30-minute blocks. (25 minutes of work + 5 minutes of breaks). This will help you focus by differentiating between work time and rest periods.</p>',268,'en'),(837,'Paste','Optimization for app stores Track the top keywords for any app and see how its search position changes over time due to their use.','<p>Get valuable data from your users by studying App Reviews and Assessments. Share data by version, country, and date to learn about bugs, follow interesting suggestions, and improve your app. Find out where and when apps have been recommended in different app stores, accurate to the day, country, device, and section. Ratings history shows how popular Auto Paste Keyboard, AutoSnap Keyboard, Copy Paste app is in the Google Play store, and lets you know how popularity changes over time.</p>',270,'en'),(838,'GIMP','GIMP, short for GNU Image Manipulation Program, is the name of a powerful and well-known free image editor that provides you with many tools for the task of high-quality image processing.','<p>The fact that it is free does not mean that it is not very powerful. GIMP has become very famous not because of luck. The program is very useful, powerful and productive.</p><p>You should emphasize the ability to flexibly customize the program to suit your work style. The program is often called a free version of Adobe Photoshop.</p><p>GIMP includes a lot of features that until now have only been the domain of very expensive programs. So now they are free, and it\'s time to start using them.</p>',271,'en'),(839,'','More than a workflow Docs Creatio is a smart enterprise content management system. A single document repository Maintain your company\'s document flow in Docs. Quickly find documents by their content or attribute values.','<p>Flexible document approval</p><p>Run and control the document approval process online. Flexible customization of the list of approvers, the ability to approve by e-mail for external counterparties. Quickly assign tasks to an employee or a group. Monitoring task fulfillment: recording expected results, having the inspector check them, and sending them back for improvement. Gantt chart reporting for successful time and resource planning. Use the ready processes of Docs ECM system and the possibilities of domestic platform Creatio, recognized all over the world. Best practices and global standards will ensure maximum efficiency in managing your company\'s processes.</p>',156,'en'),(840,'Todoist',' a web service and a set of task management software.  Tasks can also contain notes with files of any type. Tasks can be placed in projects, sorted by filter, labeled, edited, and exported.','<p>Todoist currently supports 13 computer and mobile platforms, including Microsoft Windows, Apple Mac OS X, iOS, Android, Google Chrome, Firefox, Gmail, Microsoft Outlook, Thunderbird and Postbox, and offers online synchronization and backup storage.</p><p>Todoist was founded by Amir Salihefendik and introduced in January 2007. By October 2013, the service had gained 1 million users. Todoist clients are available for Microsoft Windows, Mac OS X, Android (phones, tablets), iOS (iPhone, iPad), Linux (snap package or AppImage). Currently there is no officially supported client for Windows Phone (unofficial clients are listed below).</p>',272,'en'),(841,'NAPS2',' A handy tool for scanning documents and images With its fascination with 3D graphics and holograms, Microsoft offers Windows 10 users to scan documents with its mothballed \"Windows Fax and Scan\" program.','<p>NAPS2 is a document and image scanning program with text recognition and PDF export capabilities. NAPS2 provides users with a batch scanning tool for multipage documents, a feature for creating scanning profiles, and a simple image editor. The program supports scanning via WIA and TWAIN interfaces, gives the possibility to choose page size and resolution, set color depth, change brightness and contrast, exclude blank pages by specifying the necessary coverage and white color threshold.</p>',273,'en'),(842,'ScanLite','With this program, you can quickly scan the documents you need and save them in PDF or JPEG format.  In that case, ScanLite will help you. Not only does it take up very little space and is very easy to use','<p>Its interface is as simple and user-friendly as possible, which means that you don\'t have to deal with the settings. For example, in the latest version of the program, the scanner will be selected automatically and you only have to select the format for saving the document, its color and quality and select the saving path.</p><p>Program features:</p><p>Very simple interface.</p><p>Automatic selection of the scanner.</p><p>Change the folder for saving your scans.</p><p>Selecting the format: JPEG or PDF.</p>',275,'en'),(843,'CuneiForm','is a free open-source optical text recognition system from the Russian company Cognitive Technologies.','<p>OCR CuneiForm was developed by Cognitive Technologies as a commercial product in 1993. The system was supplied with the most popular models of scanners, MFPs and software in Russia and worldwide: Corel Draw, Hewlet-Pachard, Epson, Xerox, Samsung, Brother, Mustek, OKI, Canon, Olivetti, etc. In 2008, Cognitive Technologies opened the source codes of CuneiForm OCR. CuneiForm is positioned as a system for conversion of electronic copies of paper documents and graphic files into an editable form with the ability to preserve structure and fonts style of the original document in automatic or semi-automatic mode. The system includes two programs for single and batch processing of electronic documents.</p>',276,'en'),(844,'PaperScan',' is a program for obtaining electronic versions of documents by scanning them. The product is distributed in three versions - Free, Home, and Professional. The last two versions are paid, but include a trial period','<p>The tool allows you to work with many scanners via WIA and TWAIN technologies. In addition, PaperScan supports importing PDF files.</p><p>The program allows you to rotate, scale, crop input files, adjust brightness, contrast, and saturation, apply various filters, and convert documents to black and white. In addition, with PaperScan the user can automatically remove smudges, margins, blank areas, and stitch marks, as well as align page content that has shifted for some reason.</p>',277,'en'),(845,'','is a simple application for scanning and saving documents to your hard drive in PDF format. It requires no installation and is easy to use - all you have to do is turn on your scanner and press the scan button.','<p>With WinScan2PDF you don\'t need virtual printers. It\'s also convenient that you can select the multi-page scan option if your document is longer than one page. With this tool, sending documents via email will be much easier than before. The program works like a PDF printer, and this is really convenient because its interface gives you only three options: select a scan source, scan, and save to PDF.</p><p>Each of the buttons activates the corresponding function - you only need to select the desired scanner, and then the application will automatically detect and digitize all documents.</p>',278,'en'),(846,'','Take back control over your documents! idocs is the first electronic document management system in Kazakhstan. Electronic document management, abbreviated as EDI, is a way of organizing work with documents electronically via the Internet.','<p>Who is suitable for idocs?</p><ul><li>Small businesses with a small document turnover</li><li>For those who have a wide geography of counterparties in Kazakhstan</li><li>Medium and large businesses with a large number of document traffic per month and a significant volume of contractors</li><li>for all companies that want to abandon outdated paper documentation and switch to EDI.</li></ul><p>idocs optimizes business and simplifies document flow, using modern technology. In 2014 our team had a vision to change the way companies handle paper. We started to create a cloud platform for document exchange and in 2016 we launched an electronic document management service - idocs.</p>',157,'en'),(847,'','is a high-quality document and image scanning utility that allows users to scan almost all types of printers. It is the product of Philippe Mignard, a French inventor and businessman. ','<p>EasyScan uses standard Twain features that allow all Windows operating systems to install, run and use this software. Moreover, EasyScan\'s use of Twain distinguishes it from other similar software because it can only be used on certain systems. EasyScan software also allows you to scan documents using different scanning methods and with different image quality and clarity. The main goal of EasyScan software is to ensure that its users are compatible with the latest operating systems such as Windows 2021, XP, Vista and 7.</p>',279,'en'),(848,'','The Client for Google Translate is a free translator for Windows that allows you to translate text in browsers, office applications and other programs using Google Translate with one click.','<p>Google Translate is one of the most popular machine translation services, but translating text with an online translator is not always convenient: you have to launch a browser, open a website, copy and paste text, choose a language... Too long!</p><p>With the Google Translator Client you can translate web pages, emails and other documents without going to online translation sites or buying expensive, cumbersome software - just highlight the text with your mouse to translate.</p>',280,'en'),(849,'','is a free application for offline translation of words, text documents.  Operating system: Windows xp, vista, 7, 8.1, 10 (32/64-bit).  Interface Language: Russian, English.  In the application about six hundred thousand words and up to ninety dictionaries','<p>XETRANSLATOR is a handy translator that works without an Internet connection, recognizes characters from over 89 languages and can translate individual words, phrases and even whole text fragments. The program has a convenient two-window interface, and working with it is not difficult. XETRANSLATOR features:</p><p>user-friendly interface;</p><p>Possibility to set color and text background;</p><p>setting the font size;</p><p>instant result;</p><p>Intelligent text processing for clearer translations;</p><p>does not require an Internet connection;</p><p>ability to configure automatic translation;</p><p>large language base and vocabulary.</p>',281,'en'),(850,'','is a program for recognizing text in images and PDF files, the main purpose of which is to convert scanned documents into a form suitable for editing. The product is distributed free of charge and supports many input formats','<p>Freemore OCR has a rather modest functionality. Among the noteworthy options it has is the export of text documents to Microsoft Word, as well as password protection.</p><p>The program interface is similar to many editors. The developers themselves call it \"office-style. The menu is predominantly push-button. The controls are large icons with captions. The workspace in PDF Preview mode does not cause problems. As for the OCR mode, here the space of the program is divided into two parts. At the same time there is no possibility to change the size of the areas. Thus, in order to cover the entire source text with the eye, it is necessary to scale it.</p>',282,'en'),(851,'',' a free online OCR service, using the tesseract engine. The size of the uploaded image is limited to 2 MB. Supported formats are JPG, GIF, TIFF BMP and PDF (only the first page, soon to be supported','<p>Optical character recognition software can speed up the process, and while it is not error-free and requires you to review that text to correct any errors made in the recognition process, it can save you a lot of time.</p><p>We reviewed Project Naptha for Google Chrome only recently, which added functionality to the browser. While it works well on the web, it won\'t help you with local documents at all. FreeOCR for Windows gives you two modes of operation. You can use it to open existing image files or PDF documents, or you can use the built-in scanning feature to scan and process documents that are not already available in electronic form.</p>',283,'en'),(852,'',' is a free version of the Personal Information Manager. The product is russified and in addition supports three dozen other languages. The program is a set of all-in-one tools. For example, EsentialPIM Free includes a scheduler','<p>The program allows you to manage your own working time, organize meetings and weekends, write down ideas, make notes, and prioritize tasks.</p><p>One of the features of the manager is support for synchronization with mobile devices. This allows the user to plan and keep track of things without being right in front of the computer. EssentialPIM also has an import/export feature in case the user decides to migrate from one PC to another.</p>',285,'en'),(853,'','is a computer program and a family of electronic dictionaries developed by the Russian company ABBYY. The word \"lingvo\" means \"language\" in Esperanto, and there are articles about it in ABBYY Lingvo dictionaries (LingvoUniversal and LingvoComputer).','<p>In addition to existing dictionaries created by professional lexicographers, employees of ABBYY, and authoritative paper and electronic dictionaries, there is an extensive database of free user dictionaries in DSL (Dictionary Specification Language) supported by the ABBYY Lingvo electronic dictionary system.</p><p>Users can upload dictionaries to the Lingvo Vocabulary Association\'s website; once checked, the dictionaries will be available for downloading.</p>',286,'en'),(854,'',' is a free version of a commercial product for converting and printing documents in PDF (Adobe Portable Document Format). It is installed as a virtual printer','<p>CutePDF Writer has no graphical user interface, so it does not need to be configured. Also, since this printer is a virtual driver, you will not need to install additional Office components to create PDF files.</p><p>CutePDF Writer is free for personal and commercial use and contains no advertising modules. It is very easy to use, you just have to install it and from now on, when you want to create a PDF file from an existing one, just print it using the new \'printer\' that will appear in the list of available printers and then just select a name for the output file.</p>',287,'en'),(855,'Cominware','Comindware Tracker is the first choice for those who are on the way from Excel or Outlook-based activity tracking to a more system-oriented approach. It is a low-code workflow management software.','<p>Up-to-date Workflow Solutions</p><p>Workflow management software for every business function and department</p><p>Capital approvals - protecting investments and shortening the capital investment cycle</p><p>Procurement management - ensure proper procurement policies are followed</p><p>Claims management - allow agents to focus on people, not claims</p><p>Service request management - handle requests efficiently</p><p>Compliance and policy management - easy compliance audits</p><p>Low-code development platform allows you to build enterprise applications and solutions for all types of business needs.</p>',159,'en'),(856,'','a service for case and order management. Task-manager and CRM-system. It is an application for Windows, Mac, Android, iPhone, iPad. Allows you to make daily/weekly/monthly to-do lists, distribute tasks and control the','<p>The owner of the service is the Russian company OOO \"Organizer LeaderTask\". The company has existed since 2008. The main activity is the development of the LeaderTask service. The company also produces courses on time management and increasing efficiency. OOO \"Organizer LeaderTask\" has no foreign founders, does not attract foreign capital for development. The number of clients of the company: more than 10 000 (information as of the end of 2021). A fault-tolerant Microsoft Azure cluster is used to organize the cloud. Security is ensured by 256-bit encryption and data access over SSL.</p><p>The Microsoft Azure platform is certified to the ISO27001 security standard.</p>',289,'en'),(857,'Simple OCR','is a popular free software for text recognition in English and French. It is worth noting that if your documents contain multi-column markup, non-standard fonts, color images, or images ','<p>The program can work with documents in English and French, but will not be able to recognize characters with different superscript and subscript characters (e.g. ö, ä, é, etc.) used only in other languages.SimpleOCR is a simple program for text recognition, but unfortunately the program is not designed to work with the Russian language. If you need to get more advanced functionality will need to purchase paid add-ons. When you begin working with the program, a dialog box appears, allowing you to choose the type of work with the downloaded document, a scanned image containing printed text, or a picture with handwritten text.</p>',290,'en'),(858,'Task Coach','is a free, simple and fast open-source task and case manager for desktop and mobile systems. Startpack site data. It allows you to work with composite tasks, and the tasks themselves include a title, description, assignment','<p>Task Coach has a list of the following features:</p><p>Entry, modification and deletion of tasks and subtasks.</p><p>Inclusion of a title, description, assigning priority, substitution of start, end, and execution date, and task repeating functions with cycles.</p><p>Sorting added tasks by various attributes.</p><p>Filtering for advanced search.</p><p>Support for transferring tasks from Outlook, Claws Mail, Apple Mail or Thunderbird emails to the created task list.</p><p>Create categories for tasks and entries.</p><p>Autosave settings.</p>',292,'en'),(859,'BullZIP PDF Printer','is a program for creating PDF files from various types of electronic documents, images, web pages, and any other sources that can be sent to print. ','<p>The application is free for non-commercial use, but the free version has some functional limitations.</p><p>BullZip PDF Printer has Russian language support, suitable for Windows XP, Vista, 7, 8, 10, Server 2003/2008/2012/2016 (32 and 64 bit) operating systems. The main function of BullZip PDF Printer is to create PDF documents with various content (text, images, HTML content, etc.). As a data source the application uses files generated by different applications before sending them to the printer.</p>',293,'en'),(860,'PDFCreator','is a tool for creating PDF files from documents such as DOC. It works directly from programs such as Word. PDFCreator is a virtual printer for saving files to PDF - it has a huge number of options, from simple ','<p>However, more advanced users can create a customized PDF file by playing with the settings menu.</p><p>In addition, you can also password protect documents with three different levels of encryption, include a digital signature, and automatically send the document via email or printer.</p><p>PDFCreator has various virtual printing modes, in addition to creating PDF you can also convert PDF to PNG, JPEG, BMP, TXT, RAW and many other formats just by following the same procedure you used to create PDF.</p>',294,'en'),(861,'Cool Reader','is a program for reading electronic books in EPUB, FB2, DOC, TXT, RTF, MOBI and HTML formats. It is so simple and easy to use that it does not even require installation on your computer. Since the program is portable, it can be easily','<p>CoolReader does not leave any keys in the system registry or any other \"traces\" in the system. The book library management is very interesting in the program. Right on the main screen you can see categories of works of art that you have created, links to online catalogs with free books and a file browser panel. All these components are closely interconnected, and you can move books between them by \"dragging and dropping\". The program automatically remembers where the user left off reading, and gives you quick access to books you\'ve recently read.</p>',295,'en'),(862,'Bitobit ТрансLit','is a program for working with various texts that are written in transliteration. At the moment transliteration can be found quite often: messages and notifications of programs, some software, files, folders, text notifications','<p>Each of the modes has the ability to edit, as well as create a \"for yourself\" profile, where you can specify the main points of translation of certain characters and their combinations.</p><p>The program Bitobit TransLit has three modes, which have their own characteristics of work:</p><p>Stationary - the necessary text is copied into a special window of the program, where it is translated in the desired direction.</p><p>Mobile - this is when the copied text is translated into the desired language directly on the clipboard.</p><p>\"On the fly\" - with it the text is translated directly as it is written. It is very convenient for those who correspond in transliteration. It is also used when the Russian layout is unavailable.</p>',296,'en'),(863,'Explanary',' is a program for translating and searching for the meaning of unknown words. The product is distributed free of charge and, in addition, supports the Russian language interface. The work of the program is carried out, so to speak, in the background.','<p>The Explanary tool is capable of working with several dictionaries simultaneously and supports importing third-party reference books. If the word you need is not on the list, the program will suggest the closest variant by meaning and spelling. Explanary also supports a kind of logs, which means that it keeps a record of searched words and remembers them for possible future reference. The translator\'s interface is pretty typical. The main window is divided into two parts: the list of words in alphabetical order (on the left) and their meaning or translation (on the right). Adding and deleting dictionaries is done by checking the checkboxes next to them.</p>',297,'en'),(864,'Dictionary.NET','is a small, handy translator program that uses Google Dictionary, Google Translate, Suggest, and Wikipedia.  More than 100 languages are supported and can be used as both source and target languages. ','<p>In addition to being used to translate in the search box in the program window, it allows you to have instant translation, when reading email, documents or working on the Internet. Does not require installation.</p><p>Features Dictionary .NET:</p><p>Smart Translation feature.</p><p>Translate selected text via hot keys</p><p>Full-text and single-word translation</p><p>Text Tips</p><p>Web page translation</p><p>Document translation.</p><p>Search in Wikipedia</p><p>Listening to the pronunciation of words and sentences in the target language</p><p>List of pluggable languages</p><p>When the program is not in use, the program window changes to a clock showing the current time</p>',298,'en'),(865,'Tom Reader Russian','is a free utility for reading e-books in the Windows operating system. It allows you to read books in the most common modern formats and even listen to them thanks to support for speech synthesis.','<p>This program is a great solution for those who like to spend time with a book. It will be able to play not only text documents, but also their graphic content and sound. It is natural that for high-quality voice playback you will have to download some additional materials.</p><p>In general, all the settings of the utility are extremely simple and just as necessary, so everyone will be able to adapt this simple program to their reading needs.</p>',299,'en'),(866,'Mozilla Sunbird','a separate cross-platform application separated from the Calendar component of Mozilla Suite. Mozilla Sunbird is a completely independent application, but work is underway to integrate it with the Mozilla Firefox browser and the Mozi mail client','<p>Mozilla Sunbird is a calendar, created as a separate cross-platform application, which was spun off from the Mozilla Toolkit. The developers\' goal was to provide users with a free and powerful calendar application for everyday use. At the moment, Mozilla Sunbird is a separate, independent application, but work is underway to integrate it with the Mozilla Firefox browser and the Mozilla Thunderbird email client. The program interface is translated into most major languages, including Russian.</p>',300,'en'),(867,'QTranslate','is a free program that translates text into various languages using online services. The translation is done with just one hotkey combination (Ctrl+Q to translate the selected text in a popup window or Ctrl+W to translate','<p>The program has the ability to play (voice) text (Ctrl+E to voice the selected text).</p><p>Note! The program translates text with the help of online translators, so you need an Internet connection.</p><p>The program has two modes of text translation with the mouse (it is enabled/disabled by a single mouse click on the program\'s icon in the tray):</p><p>Show Icon (You select the text in any program, the program icon appears near the cursor. Click the icon and a pop-up window with the translation of selected text will appear);</p><p>Show translation (You select the text in any program and the pop-up window with the translation of the selected text appears immediately).</p>',301,'en'),(868,'Dictionarist',' free translator with which you can perform one-click translation. Automatic translation is performed by moving the mouse pointer to the word of interest and pressing the appropriate key combination on the keyboard and mouse.','<p>The program does not require Internet access.</p><p>The main features of Dictionarist:</p><p>Automatic translation with a single click;</p><p>The Internet is not required for operation;</p><p>Pronunciation of words to be translated;</p><p>Use in title bar mode;</p><p>Support of a large number of languages;</p><p>Wide vocabulary database</p><p>The main advantage of this translator program is that it does not require an internet connection in its work. Dictionarist works quickly and supports a large number of foreign languages.</p>',302,'en'),(869,'Mars Notebook',' is a handy notebook whose sections have a tree-like structure. The application has a built-in text editor with support for spell checking. In it you can format links, pictures, numbering, markers, create tables','<p>To install the application on your device you need to register on the manufacturer\'s official website or download a license.</p><p>Main features of Mars Notebook</p><p>tree-like structure with unlimited possibilities of attachments;</p><p>up-to-date text editor;</p><p>Possibility to import and export documents in the formats Word, HTML, XML, Windows Write, RTF, text files, including Unicode system;</p><p>it is possible to export the whole database or some of its parts to CHM;</p><p>password protection;</p><p>possibility to save data and its sections in one file for further convenient transfer to another device;</p>',303,'en'),(870,'Cloud Translator',' A free program for translating texts and user interface elements of other programs. Supports pronunciation of phrases in different languages, text search in Wikipedia and Google and other useful service functions. You do not need to install','<p>Cloud Translator features:</p><p>Translation of texts from all Internet browsers, office and e-mail applications, messaging programs and almost any text editors that allow you to highlight text.</p><p>Translation of buttons, checkboxes, text fields and other elements of the user interface that represent a separate window.</p><p>Ability to choose a translator.</p><p>History of translations.</p><p>Pronunciation of selected phrases in the selected language.</p><p>Ability to customize control panels, keyboard shortcuts, and support for design themes.</p>',304,'en'),(871,'Dicter','is a free online translator that allows you to hotkey translate selected text in any Windows application into 48 languages and vice versa.','<p>Also, the program allows you to listen to the translated text in any language and copy it to the clipboard for later use.</p><p>Advanced mode allows you to use the translator as a professional program for making large translations, with the ability to edit, dubbing and copying of the translated text.</p><p>Translation is carried out through Google Translate, which provides high speed and quality of translation.</p><p>In the settings you can change the font size, as well as set your own combination of \"hotkeys\".</p>',305,'en'),(872,'ImTranslator','is a convenient plugin for browsers, which is an online translator of 2,652 language combinations. It should be noted that the program is well equipped with such modules as a translation editor, a virtual keyboard, a spell-checker','<p>ImTranslator is an extension for Google Chrome, Opera, Yandex.browser and Mozilla Firefox, which is an online translator for more than 90 languages.</p><p>Key features of the program:</p><p>Online translation of over 2,652 language combinations;</p><p>Virtual keyboard allowing to enter symbols in more than 40 languages;</p><p>Built-in dictionary;</p><p>Spell Check;</p><p>Decoding of unreadable Russian text in the appropriate encoding;</p><p>Ability to display the Russian words in Latin characters;</p><p>Built-in audio module \"Text To Speach\";</p><p>Print original and translated text;</p><p>Ability to send translated texts by E-mail.</p>',306,'en'),(873,'EveryLang','allows you to translate any text, check the spelling, switch the layout in manual and automatic mode, has a layout indicator in different views, works with the clipboard, uses templates of texts, keeps a diary of the typed text,','<p>EveryLang will significantly increase the speed of word processing. It will provide new opportunities to save time on routine procedures.</p><p>Text translation is done with the help of Google, Microsoft and Yandex services, which translate the text into any language you need.</p><p>In the main window you can translate text, select services and languages, change their places. By default, the translation is in the language, which is the main language in Windows. Spell check is implemented with the service ORFO, and there is no need to choose a language for checking, the system itself will determine it and give the result.</p>',307,'en'),(874,'AlReader',' \"reader\" for text files and e-books in various formats (abw, sxw, odt, docx, doc, rtf, pdb, prc, html, txt, chm, etc.). The program allows you to configure several profiles for more comfortable reading (e.g., the profile \"night\" - with more','<p>AlReader is a handy program for reading e-books and various texts in full-screen mode. Many popular file formats are supported, such as HTML, CHM, TXT, RTF, PDB/PRC, DOC, DOCX, ODT, SXW, ABW and others.</p><p>Main features of the program:</p><p>\"Day\"/\"Night\" profiles (profile includes text font settings: size, bold, anti-aliasing, color: background, text and status bar) - up to 8 profiles</p><p>reading HTML, RTF, FB2, DOC, DOCX, ODT, SXW, ABW, ZABW, RB, TCR - support text styles, images, navigation links, content. (DOC format not with pictures yet).</p><p>CHM reading - experimental support.</p><p>TXT, PDB/PRC (PalmDOC, zTXT mode 1) - text only.</p><p>to read from ZIP and GZ archives.</p><p>reading RAR archives</p>',308,'en'),(875,'ToolTip Translator','is a text translator, designed for instant translation while reading text.  To use the program, you need to highlight the desired text, press the special function key - and next to the mouse cursor you will immediately','<p>Thanks to Yandex.Translation API the program can work in any browser and \"knows\" how to translate all texts contained in text editors (for example, MS Office, DjVu, Acrobat Reader).</p><p>The program cannot replace a full-fledged translator with databases, but its main purpose is to help those users who know a foreign language a little, but have some difficulties when reading without a dictionary. Thanks to this utility you will be able to find out the translation of a certain word, sentence or paragraph without having to use another translation program and without visiting online translation links (e.g. Google Translator, Yandex.Translation).</p>',310,'en'),(876,'NeoDic','is a free program that helps you translate unfamiliar words and phrases by simply moving the mouse cursor over the word - Context translation. Context translation - allows you to translate unfamiliar words and phrases simply by placing the mouse cursor ','<p>This type of translation is very convenient when reading Internet pages, reading the help system, chatting, text layout, etc. The program works in all applications. Using this product, you will get a translation of unfamiliar words instantly. The program will help you \"surf\" on foreign Internet sites, communicate with people in different languages, translate extracts from technical literature and much more. In addition, the application can automatically detect the language and choose the right dictionary, and also allows you to use sdict dictionaries.</p>',311,'en'),(877,'Soda PDF',' A program that allows you to create, convert and edit a variety of brochures, resumes, flyers, advertisements and any educational material in PDF format.','<p>The main features of Soda PDF</p><p>User-friendly interface allows you to start working immediately after installation.</p><p>Ability to convert more than three hundred different formats to PDF in one click.</p><p>Professional forms and templates.</p><p>Fully compatible with any PDF files.</p><p>Easy-to-use editing tool.</p><p>Manage the digital signature of the document.</p><p>3D mode gives the impression of working with a real book.</p><p>Small size and high speed of work.</p>',312,'en'),(878,'Calibre','free and open source software for reading, creating and storing e-books in a digital library of different formats. The program has the ability to synchronize with e-book reading devices ','<p>Caliber is a tool for working with e-books. All information about books (title, author, cover, grade, tags, release date, publisher) is stored in a database. When you add a book to the database, all information about it is added, and the book file is placed in the library folder. In addition, you can get information about the book from the Internet with the help of the ISBN. Supported formats are AZW, AZW1, AZW2, AZW3, CBR, CBZ, CHM, EPUB, FB2, HTML, IMP, LIT, LRF, LRX, MOBI, ODT, OEBZIP, OPF, PDB, PDF, PML, PMLZ, PRC, RAR, RB, RTF, SNB, TPZ, TXT and ZIP.</p>',313,'en'),(879,'FBreader','is a program distributed free of charge. Its main purpose is to provide the user with a comfortable reading of electronic books. The program works with the formats FB2, ePub, TCR, RTF, OEB, doc, HTML and others. ','<p>The reader works on Windows, Linux, iOS, Mac OS and even BlackBerry. In addition to reading books and magazines in FBReader, you can create your own libraries and filter books into different categories. Such a system will make it easier to navigate and help you create a personalized digital library.</p><p>Free FBReader in Russian hasn\'t been updated for a long time. The official website says that a new beta version 0.99 will be available in early 2015. There is no beta version or any news for September 2018.</p>',314,'en'),(880,'Adobe Reader','allows you to do more than just open and view PDF files. Comment on documents with ease using notes, enter text directly on the page, underline, underline and strikethrough text, and draw by hand. ','<p>Acrobat Reader is connected to the Adobe Document Cloud, so you can work with PDF documents from any device. You can also store files in Box, Dropbox, Microsoft OneDrive and Google Drive. As always, the free and even more powerful Acrobat Reader mobile app</p><p>gives you all the tools you need to view, annotate, sign</p><p>and send PDF files - even on the go. Add Acrobat Pro DC to it for even more features.</p><p>Edit, create, export, organize and merge files right on your tablet</p><p>or smartphone.</p>',315,'en'),(881,'Open Office','Microsoft is not the only one offering a full-featured suite of office productivity applications. You can also enjoy other free programs that provide almost the same functions.','<p>We can enjoy Openoffice.org absolutely for free, it\'s 100% compatible, and you don\'t have to pay for features you can use for free. In this package you will find everything you need for your work - text editor, database editor, presentation creator, ...</p><p>The application integrates with Windows and is one of the most stable and fastest solutions.</p><p>The project is developed under the GNU license, so access and updates for the software are provided.</p>',316,'en'),(882,'ICE Book Reader Pro','A program for easy reading of electronic texts (books). Can read from TXT, HTML, XML, RTF files, Microsoft Word documents, PALM books (.PDB and .PRC), PSION/EPOC books (.TCR), Microsoft Reader books (.LIT), Microsoft HELP files (.PRC).','<p>Very smooth scrolling, moreover two scrolling modes are allowed - with constant and variable speed depending on text density, function of font readability improvement, full support of all encodings and Unicode, automatic text reformatting, full-screen anti-aliasing with different masks (2x2, 3x3 and 4x4) making reading more comfortable, and also internal archivers (ZIP, RAR, ARJ, LZH, HA). Also possible to use as TXT-HTML, HTML-TXT, TXT-DOC, DOC-TXT, PDB-TXT, LIT-TXT, FB2-TXT etc. file converter with conversion of different code pages.</p>',317,'en'),(883,'DjVu Reader','is a program designed for viewing files in DjVu format. The program supports two languages: Russian and English. Two languages are included in its support, as it is written by Russian-speaking developers.','<p>Supports viewing in both single-window and double-window modes.</p><p>Wide adjustment of image brightness and contrast makes it possible to choose the optimal position for the user\'s eyes, in which it will be convenient and comfortable to read from the computer screen. Full indexing of not only the pages, but also of the content is realized.</p><p>DjVuReader supports copying of both texts and images to the clipboard.</p><p>DjVuReader now enables to open all tabs in one window, which means you don\'t need to keep many copies of programs in your system tray. This support is implemented in the same way as in modern browsers, which have been supporting this function for a long time</p>',318,'en'),(884,'Okdo PDF Splitter Free','is a utility for quickly dividing PDF files into separate parts. The program offers a wide range of options for dividing PDF documents - into individual pages, files of several pages, part of a page, even/odd pages','<p>This product does not require specific programs for PDF processing, such as Adobe Reader and others. In addition, the program functionality supports splitting password-protected files, allows you to create separate output folders for each PDF source, and has a number of other useful features. The program interface is quite simple, making it possible even for a complete beginner to master the utility - all you have to do is to select the file to be split, specify the splitting type and the folder where the new documents will be saved.</p><p>Okdo PDF Splitter Free has a limit on the size of a split PDF file - not more than 100 pages.</p>',320,'en'),(885,'Okdo Split Merge PDF Free',' is a program that can divide and merge a variety of documents and images in PDF format. By fine-tuning all the parameters and functions of the program, you can achieve a different range of converted pages.','<p>You will get a fully readable and high-quality image in your source documents. The program allows you to save sizes of margins, tables, text format, original links, images and similar parameters. To work, you need to select the desired task, specify where to save the source file and click the appropriate button. Okdo PDF Merger Free is a powerful utility for merging multiple PDF files into one PDF document. Using this tool to create a new PDF file, you can select any pages in the original PDF documents, set the range of pages according to the necessary requirements.</p>',321,'en'),(886,'LibreOffice','is a powerful office suite, fully compatible with 32/64-bit systems. Translated into more than 30 languages. Supports most popular operating systems, including GNU/Linux, Microsoft Windows and Mac OS X.','<p>LibreOffice is free and open source, so you can download, use, and learn LibreOffice for free. LibreOffice is free for private, educational or commercial use. It can be used without any license fees by your family, friends, co-workers, students, employees and so on. The office suite contains a word processor, a spreadsheet processor, a program for preparing and viewing presentations, a vector graphics editor, a database management system and a formula editor.</p>',322,'en'),(887,'','PDF is used more and more as a common format when reading, creating and sending text documents. The well-known format is used by millions of people, and it is a good way if you want to send documents to print, if you want to save your','<p>There are many programs for viewing this type of documents, such as the original Adobe program, but there are also many people who like to try new programs that are sometimes even better or faster than the official ones. If you want to try a new product, PDF-XChange Viewer is one of the recommended ones.</p><p>It includes all the standard features found in PDF viewers: zoom in and out, rotate, open with URL,... and it\'s very lightweight, works very well, even with older computers.</p>',323,'en'),(888,'',' installs a virtual printer on your system that allows you to create PDF files.  With PrimoPDF it is not difficult at all to create PDF files. In fact, it\'s very simple and... totally free.','<p>PrimoPDF is a free program for quick and easy conversion of files to PDF (Portable Document Format). All you need to do is select the document you want to convert to pdf, print it out and choose Primo PDF printer instead of the usual printer. Then you will see a menu where you will be able to customize the properties of the file you are creating. In addition, you will be able to password protect your file, so that only the people you tell the password to can open the file. Finally, you can add an author and comments to the file.</p>',324,'en'),(889,'','program is designed for reading aloud text files. Any speech synthesizer installed on your computer can be used to reproduce the sounds of the human voice.','<p>Speech playback can be controlled using the standard buttons similar to those found in any multimedia program (\"play/stop/stop\"). The program can read aloud the contents of the clipboard, show the text contained in the files, change font and color settings, control the reading process from the system tray or using keyboard shortcuts, pronounce the text typed on the keyboard, check spelling, divide a text file into several smaller files, search for homographs.</p>',325,'en'),(890,'','is a file viewer specifically designed to work with technical documents.  The program provides a unique environment for working with a variety of file formats, such as PDF, TIFF or DjVu.','<p>Moreover, it has many tools and options to structure them and view their contents properly.</p><p>With STDU Viewer you will be able to open many files at once, tag pages, use bookmarks, search for text, copy images or text,...</p><p>In conclusion, the best thing about STDU Viewer is the built-in content viewer which gives you an excellent opportunity to analyze any file and view hidden information or additional data such as headings, chapters or other organizational structures.</p>',327,'en'),(891,'',' A cross-platform runtime environment that allows developers to use HTML/CSS, Ajax, JavaScript, Adobe Flash Professional and Adobe Flex software, and the ActionScript language to deploy','<p>The coherent and flexible application development environment for various devices and platforms provided by Adobe AIR, a core component of the Adobe Flash Platform, helps designers and developers unleash all their creativity.</p><p>Adobe AIR features:</p><p>Using AIR, you can easily transfer a finished HTML or Adobe Flex application to a user\'s computer.</p><p>Applications have access to the file system, clipboard, support for multiple windows, drag and drop technology.</p><p>It is supported by mobile operating systems Android, BlackBerry Tablet OS and iOS, as well as TV devices.</p>',328,'en'),(892,'','Free, compact and fast program for viewing files in PDF, ePub, FB2, MOBI, XPS, DjVu, CHM, CBZ and CBR. It has a simple and unobtrusive interface, which will not make the slightest bit of difficulty to understand even novice users.','<p>Sumatra PDF has a minimalist design, is compact and fast to work with. The nice feature is the ability to edit files opened in Sumatra PDF using another program (Sumatra does not block the file). It is several times faster than Adobe Reader while consuming minimum system resources. Another advantage of Sumatra PDF is that it requires no installation, which allows to run the program from external USB memory sticks. Support for keyboard shortcuts makes working with this program even faster and more convenient. The program is designed for portable use: it does not require installation and can be run from a flash card</p>',329,'en'),(893,'',' a free set (freeware) of office applications for creating, editing and sharing texts, spreadsheets, presentations and other closed-source documents.','<p>IBM Lotus Symphony uses OpenOffice.org technologies and Eclipse free integrated development platform for modular cross-platform applications, supports ODF (OpenDocument), ISO 26300 standards.</p><p>In 2008, it was named Product of the Year in the Office Productivity Software category by Datamation Magazine[3]. Other contenders included OpenOffice.org 2.3.1 and ThinkFree Office. A variety of plug-ins are available[4]. PDF export and VBA (Visual Basic for Application) support are implemented.</p>',330,'en'),(894,'','is the smallest PDF viewer (reader) for viewing and printing PDF files and converting PDF to TXT, BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG, WMF, EMF, EPS files. Its size is less than one megabyte, and installation is almost instantaneous','<p>Cool PDF Reader is a utility that allows you to view PDF files as well as print and convert them to EPS, EMF, WMF, JPG, TXT, BMP, GIF, and PNG formats.Another advantage of Cool PDF Reader is the ability to show PDF documents in slideshow mode.</p><p>Cool PDF Reader main features</p><p>Reads and prints PDF.</p><p>Converts PDF to BMP, JPG, GIF, PNG, WMF, EMF, EPS.</p><p>Extracts PDF to TXT.</p><p>Supports PDF files of any version.</p><p>Works with over 68 languages.</p><p>Enlarges and reduces.</p><p>Page through pages on screen.</p><p>Shows PDF document slides in full screen mode.</p><p>Small in size, only 655KB.</p>',331,'en'),(895,'','WinDjView is a powerful, easy-to-use and feature-rich program for users who need to work with DjVu files. This is a graphical format which allows you to compress electronic files without loss of quality.','<p>The application was originally developed for reading e-books in DjVu format. However, the program is endowed by the developer with many useful features that allow you to use it fully, for example, you can make notes and create an unlimited number of bookmarks. The application is free and has a modern, intuitive interface, smooth page scrolling and handy print functions. To decorate documents in DjVu format, the application uses the DjVuLibre library.</p>',332,'en'),(896,'Кладовой','This is a service for warehouse automation. Drawing on more than 10 years of experience in warehouse automation based on 1C, we have created our own product. The service provides automation similar to the implementation of WMS, only with minimal costs.','<p>To reduce the costs of implementing and using the Pantry service allows:</p><p>Using an existing 1C configuration (or renting it from the cloud)</p><p>Using a smartphone instead of a POS or barcode scanner.</p><p>If you already have a 1C configuration (Trade Management or Integrated automation), you can quickly and cost-effectively automate warehouse operations.</p><p>In the absence of configuration you can rent it on our cloud service. And it also will not require significant investments.</p>',422,'en'),(897,'','a family of multifunctional extensible text editors.  The original EMACS was written in 1976 by Richard Stallman and Guy Steele as a set of editing macros','<p>Emacs is a fairly advanced text editor. It provides tools that give you \"more than a simple paste or delete\", namely:</p><p>Viewing and editing 2 or more files (with the ability to move text between files).</p><p>In addition to traditional editing, tools that make it easier to develop programs in different programming languages (C, Fortran, Perl,....), such as: highlighting syntactically different elements in color, automatic creation of indents in programs, finding parentheses ; finding function names in all the files that make up the project (in particular, finding the function definition), automatic completion of names.</p>',333,'en'),(898,'Rozmovlyalka',' is a program for scoring Ukrainian-language texts. It differs from other similar programs by its full support of the Ukrainian language, the possibility of scoring texts with several voices and their rather high quality.','<p>Rozmovlyalka can be useful: for children to read books; for students and adults to read fiction and business papers; to create simple educational, entertainment and presentation programs; to provide reference information by voice in automated information systems; for learners of Ukrainian in non-Ukrainian environment; for the visually impaired. Main features of Rozmovlyalka:</p><p>- High quality and naturalness of the voice.</p><p>- Voices dialogues and scenes with several participants with different voices.</p><p>- Synchronously with the reading of the text shows images.</p>',334,'en'),(899,'DoPDF','is installed as a virtual PDF driver for your printer, so that after successful installation it appears in the list of your Printers and Faxes. To create a PDF file, you just need to print the document on a free do PDF converter.','<p>Open your document (with Microsoft Word, WordPad, NotePad or any other application), click Print and select doPDF printer. The program will ask you where to save the PDF file and after it finishes writing the file, the PDF file will automatically open in your standard PDF viewer. The video below shows you how to create a PDF file from a Microsoft Word document (word to pdf):</p>',335,'en'),(900,'Rnote','Free and functional text editor. The program allows you to work simultaneously with several documents, quickly translate text into other encodings, there is a function of autosave and encryption','<p>In addition, there is support for plugins, a variety of text formats, there are \"Beginner\", \"Read Only\" and \"Programmer\" modes, as well as a module for viewing images and much more.</p><p>What\'s new in Rnote 2.1.0.189?</p><p>Expanded the C++ syntax highlighting dictionary (from 73 to 87).</p><p>Optimized word count.</p><p>Slightly improved performance.</p><p>Ability to select program when undoing associations.</p><p>Added filters *.cxx;*.sgml;*.ml;*.pl;*.pm;*.py;*.rb;*.rbw;*.vsm;*.sha;*.las;*.lasso;*.jsp;*.stm;*.xhtml;*.xhtm;*.php3;*.phtml;*.info;*.docm.</p><p>Support for inserting *.png images into text.</p>',336,'en'),(901,'Abiword','is a free word processor distributed under the GNU General Public License. It is supported on Linux, Mac OS X, Microsoft Windows, ReactOS, SkyOS, QNX, and other platforms. It is used by default in Debian, Xubuntu, and Lubu distributions','<p>AbiWord is a word processing tool similar to Microsoft Word. It is ideal for creating, editing and printing documents, messages, letters, memos, etc.</p><p>AbiWord is part of a larger project known as AbiSource, which was started by SourceGear Corporation. Its goal was to develop a cross-platform set of open-source office programs. The project began with the AbiWord word processor. Its source code was deliberately and carefully written so that AbiWord would continue to work on virtually any operating system with a minimum of time spent on porting.</p>',338,'en'),(902,'AkelPad',' an open-source text editor designed to be small and fast. It can serve as an alternative to the standard Notepad included with Windows.','<p>Features:</p><p>Single-window mode (SDI), multi-window mode (MDI);</p><p>Editing files over 64K in size (in general, the size of an editable file is theoretically unlimited);</p><p>Full Unicode string support on Unicode systems (NT/2000/XP/2003);</p><p>Handling of Unicode encodings (UTF-16 little endian, UTF-16 big endian, UTF-8);</p><p>Handling of any system installed charset;</p><p>Handling of DOS/Windows and Unix line feed formats (including saving);</p><p>Preview of files opening;</p><p>Correct pseudo-graphics display;</p><p>Editing files with \"Read Only\" attribute;</p><p>Warning when attempting to open a binary file;</p><p>Multi-level rollback of actions;</p>',339,'en'),(903,'Opentext Documentum','ECM system for large companies. Contains a complete set of tools for managing any content, document flow, business processes. Provides a web interface with extensive collaboration and social interaction capabilities.','Documentum is the world market leader in ECM (Enterprise Content Management) systems. It is a full-featured platform designed for management of unstructured enterprise information (various types of documents, digital media data, content of Internet sites). Documentum platform allows not only to manage enterprise documents at all life cycle stages, but also to solve tasks of complex automation of various business processes, providing process-oriented connection of various information systems.',160,'en'),(904,'Scribus','is a free and free cross-platform open-source application for publishing - visual layout of documents, preparation for printing. The program is similar in concept to Adobe InDesign, Microsoft Publisher and Qua','<p>Scribus provides text and table formatting, vector drawing tools, and management of imported external images. In addition, there is support for a large number of file types from other publishing systems, document formats, and graphics using import/export filters (Ghostscript software is required in some cases). Special features include colorblind emulation and rendering of LaTeX or Lilypond markup languages.Sctibus is available to Linux, UNIX, OS X, OS/2, eCS, Haiku, and Windows users and is distributed under the GNU General Public License.</p>',340,'en'),(905,'WinPad XP',' is a very powerful and convenient text editor, equipped with many useful and necessary for text editing functions. The main difference between WinPad XP and other editors is the ability to switch between functions using tabs','<p>WinPad XP is designed to work with various programming languages. The program works with five Russian-language encodings, which can also be switched using tabs.</p><p>WinPad XP has the ability to highlight the syntax of different text. You can edit several documents of different encodings at once, which are displayed in tabs, which is very convenient when translating text from one syntax to another. The number of bookmarks is limited to nine. The program can simultaneously perform a variety of operations with multiple files.</p>',341,'en'),(906,'Fit FAKTURA','If you have a one-person company, you have to issue invoices. You can do this in a spreadsheet, but it\'s much easier to use a special invoicing program.','<p>The Fit FAKTURA program is one of the most popular free tools. Allows you to issue VAT sales invoices / Pro Forms / Purchase on credit, sale / purchase, receipts, orders. Works with fiscal printers. Saves documents in its database and prints. If we want to save the invoice in PDF format, we need to download a free add-on.</p>',342,'en'),(907,'Мотив','DOCFLOW \"MOTIV\": Electronic document management Supports the full document lifecycle: from registration to sending to the archive. Accelerates document approval by 20 times. Convenient routing and fast interface.','<p>Records Management</p><p>EDMS \"Motiv\" streamlines work with any type of documents.</p><p>Automatically generates a document from an e-mail to work with external users.</p><p>Saves all actions on the document.</p><p>It has a comprehensive mechanism of reports and analytics for accurate management decisions.</p><p>Guarantees document security by means of an electronic signature.</p><p>Reconciliation</p><p>Set up in a few clicks a redirection to the required specialist depending on the parameters of the incoming document.</p><p>Delegate the preparation of draft resolutions to assistants. When a draft resolution is approved, a document execution task is automatically created.</p>',162,'en'),(908,'TextExpander','will save time for everyone who works a lot with texts and has to enter the same information often. With it you can set up keyboard shortcuts, which will instantly unfold into a predetermined text of any size','<p>Work faster and smarter by using powerful keyboard shortcuts and TextExpander abbreviations to simplify and speed up everything you type. Create powerful text snippets to save you time so that whatever you type is a short abbreviation and TextExpander does the rest of the typing for you. Keep your whole team communicating effectively and consistently. Share snippets of messages, captions, and descriptions with everyone who works with you on projects.</p>',343,'en'),(909,'FossDoc','FossDoc - ваш надежный инструмент для решения сложных задач управления документопотоками. Наглядность процессов обработки документов, повышение эффективности работы сотрудников, оптимизация затрат предприятия.','<p>FossDoc electronic document management system is a solution based on FossLook platform designed for creation of electronic archive of documents, organization of corporate document management (workflow) and automation of business processes at enterprises, institutions and organizations of any type of activity. The program allows you to solve a large number of tasks, the implementation of which is entrusted to the appropriate modules. The system can be easily reconfigured to meet the specifics of each particular enterprise.</p>',164,'en'),(910,'Optima-Workflow','\"OPTIMA-WorkFlow\" is a comprehensive application platform for creating solutions in the field of document management, which integrates information technology from leading Russian and foreign manufacturers.','<p>The integration approach, based on the use of ready-to-use and proven software components, allows the \"OPTIMA-WorkFlow\" to use the capabilities of software solutions and information technologies, which have earned a reputation as the leading in their class, during the product development.</p><p>Application as a server component of \"OPTIMA-WorkFlow\" modern database management systems (Microsoft SQL Server or Oracle Database) provides all the advantages of using \"client-server\" architecture, reliable and stable interaction with the resources of computer networks and operating systems, the ability to scale solutions and to function in distributed corporate networks.</p>',165,'en'),(911,'CompanyMedia','CompanyMedia reflects InterTrust\'s twenty-five years of experience in creating document management systems. Full-cycle electronic document management, work with citizens\' requests, and control of executive discipline.','CompanyMedia is a corporate system for managing documents, tasks and personal productivity. CompanyMedia is based on the principles of end-to-end electronic document management, which allows you to save evidence of the organization activities in the interests of external and internal regulation, analysis and management decision-making, staff performance evaluation, the formation of best management practices. Territorially distributed organizations receive the greatest benefits from the system implementation.',166,'en'),(912,'Босс-референт','The BOSS-Referent system was developed to automate the management document and office workflow. Created in 1996, BOSS-Referent is one of the leaders on the Russian market of ECM solutions.','Users of the electronic document management system BOSS-Referent are federal and regional authorities, state unitary enterprises, commercial companies, including both holdings with a large branch structure and small organizations. Document management automation with BOSS-Referent leads to increased productivity of employees, facilitates access to information for making management decisions, improves managerial discipline and, consequently, improves the overall quality of management.',167,'en'),(913,'Docuware','Software for document management and document automation. For business everywhere. Business happens everywhere: in the office, on the road, at home. DocuWare digitizes and protects your information for seamless person-to-person exchange.','<p>DocuWare provides cloud document management solutions and workflow automation software that allows you to digitize, protect and work with your business documents and then streamline the processes behind your business.</p><p>By getting rid of wasted time and uncertainty in your processes, your team can focus on work that improves productivity and profits. DocuWare is ideal for distributed and remote teams that need to work at maximum productivity.</p>',168,'en'),(914,'DocLogix','\"DocLogix\" is an electronic document management system designed to manage correspondence, contracts, meetings, purchases and other documents or tasks, and to automate related processes.','<p>\"DocLogix is used by about 35,000 users. Our customers are 300 organizations in the government, banking, insurance, energy, manufacturing and other sectors. The product is available in 11 countries.</p><p>Functionality of the DocLogix EDM platform Document templates Document version control Storing and archiving of documents Support of various electronic document standards Document scanning with OCR Preview Digital and mobile signature Task management Process automation User management Powerful search engine Reporting Adaptation without programming Multilingual interface Access via web browsers Integration with Microsoft Office Mobile access (Mobile application allows working with DocLogix via mobile phone)</p>',169,'en'),(915,'PayDox',' PayDox electronic document management and collaboration support system provides integrated management of business processes and documents of the enterprise and has unlimited possibilities for customization according to customers\' requirements.','<p>Electronic document management PayDox EDMS and PayDox CRM are chosen by organizations that need a guaranteed successful result in a short time. We perform survey of business processes of your company at our own expense, we don\'t require advanced payment for PayDox implementation, and use the principle of payment for ready working system, which allows you to 100% exclude any project risks. You have nothing urgent when your documents are in order, and PayDox notifies you in time when orders, orders, contracts and payment documents are due, and informs you in real time about the situation with sales.</p>',171,'en');
